Package: oneKP
Title: Retrieve Data from the 1000 Plants Initiative (1KP)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Zebulun", "Arendsee", email = "zbwrnz@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:
    The 1000 Plants Initiative (www.onekp.com) has sequenced the transcriptomes
    of over 1000 plant species. This package allows these sequences to be
    retrieved by species or recursively by clade. Scientific names and NCBI
    taxonomy IDs are both supported.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
Imports:
    rvest,
    curl,
    readr,
    tidyr,
    magrittr,
    dplyr,
    xml2,
    methods,
    rlang,
    taxizedb
Remotes:
    arendsee/taxizedb
